      <Meanings>
        <Meaning id="37721a0e-5e98-49a6-9f8e-fe196e8b7572" type="Noun">
          <Vi>Cây cỏ timothy, một loài cỏ lâu năm, có giá trị làm thức ăn cho gia súc.</Vi>
          <En>A perennial grass (Phleum pratense) widely grown for hay and pasture, especially in cool temperate regions.</En>
          <Example>Timothy hay is a common feed for horses due to its high fiber and low protein content.</Example>
          <IsArchaic>false</IsArchaic>
          <Situations>
            <Situation id="316ad44b-e727-4f61-851a-42aceecacc57">
              <Vi>Nông dân thu hoạch timothy để làm cỏ khô cho bò sữa.</Vi>
              <En>Farmers harvest timothy grass to make hay for dairy cattle.</En>
            </Situation>
            <Situation id="5ca471fe-b78c-40d1-ad9f-d071380c64fe">
              <Vi>Bác sĩ thú y khuyên dùng cỏ timothy cho ngựa bị dị ứng phấn hoa.</Vi>
              <En>A veterinarian recommends timothy hay for horses with pollen allergies.</En>
            </Situation>
          </Situations>
